{"tid":1105570,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"韓在美開嗆：3任台大法律系總統 讓台灣經濟殘廢","createTime":"2019-04-14T04:11:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-14T15:32:42.000Z","uid":141151,"like":1,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"2e7cc35cbeb6c309e3afe95f462bf2a1c83b83ea","tid":1105570,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T04:11:39.000Z","msg":"韓在美開嗆：3任台大法律系總統 讓台灣經濟殘廢<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E9%9F%93%E5%9C%A8%E7%BE%8E%E9%96%8B%E5%97%86%EF%BC%9A3%E4%BB%BB%E5%8F%B0%E5%A4%A7%E6%B3%95%E5%BE%8B%E7%B3%BB%E7%B8%BD%E7%B5%B1-%E8%AE%93%E5%8F%B0%E7%81%A3%E7%B6%93%E6%BF%9F%E6%AE%98%E5%BB%A2-015032331.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E9%259F%2593%25E5%259C%25A8%25E7%25BE%258E%25E9%2596%258B%25E5%2597%2586%25EF%25BC%259A3%25E4%25BB%25BB%25E5%258F%25B0%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E6%25B3%2595%25E5%25BE%258B%25E7%25B3%25BB%25E7%25B8%25BD%25E7%25B5%25B1-%25E8%25AE%2593%25E5%258F%25B0%25E7%2581%25A3%25E7%25B6%2593%25E6%25BF%259F%25E6%25AE%2598%25E5%25BB%25A2-015032331.html&d=3CWkRSL9Alw2F84R5nIU8s2proQWM4oxojYLcFbEfDU%3D&h=86ef0a10\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E9%9F%93%E5%9C%A8%E7%BE%8E%E9%96%8B%E5%97%86%EF%BC%9A3%E4%BB%BB%E5%8F%B0%E5%A4%A7%E6%B3%95%E5%BE%8B%E7%B3%BB%E7%B8%BD%E7%B5%B1-%E8%AE%93%E5%8F%B0%E7%81%A3%E7%B6%93%E6%BF%9F%E6%AE%98%E5%BB%A2-015032331.html</a><br />\n<br />\n國民黨北市議會黨團昨才傳出將在17日（周三）率先提案，直接徵召高雄市長韓國瑜參選2020總統，目前人在美國洛杉磯招商的韓則針對韓流現象，直指「3個台大法律系總統幹完，台灣的經濟競爭力基本上已經殘廢了」，意有所指的發言引發網友議論！<br />\n<br />\n綜合媒體報導，韓國瑜表示「韓流」只是代名詞，關鍵是民心思變；台灣過去3任總統都是台大法律系，3個台大法律系總統幹完，台灣的經濟競爭力基本上已經殘廢了；現在新加坡國民所得將近6萬美金，香港4、5萬美金，澳門也有近8萬美金，台灣人還在2.4至2.5萬美金，「所有藉口都不能掩飾我這句話，台灣鬼混2、30年」，少數人光鮮亮麗，過著很好的生活，但很多中低收入戶卻苦得受不了。<br />\n<br />\n韓國瑜覺得韓流現象若有一點小小意義，在於提醒台灣當前政治人物一定要以人民為本，回到民本而不是在權力2字打轉，不停用各種抹黑、扭曲和造謠繼續獲得政權。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"748d9e2982a561cd12a2e2d9a1624f42304ea792","tid":1105570,"uid":123456,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T04:12:37.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">同child登仔一樣<br />\n反理智<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"b77fbb9073e9f6565dddbe8d1e04534a29b2072d","tid":1105570,"uid":77092,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T04:15:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"925905ceed11d23a7e1567a928327d7e8446cc2e","tid":1105570,"uid":157994,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T04:15:34.000Z","msg":"韓水魚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8239d92caa03e30673eb0084d3a739a34230755a","tid":1105570,"uid":44916,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T04:17:18.000Z","msg":"香港咪又係「很多中低收入戶卻苦得受不了」"},{"pid":"2621910f32350d7fe4acc8422be59283622ceaf1","tid":1105570,"uid":54959,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T04:19:44.000Z","msg":"關台大法律系咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e22d050ddbf8575cce7384f367d96f2bad2bfa85","tid":1105570,"uid":26553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T04:21:27.000Z","msg":"澳門也有近8萬美金<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"378c81f271b8457e169b04c388d6a01a228d5e78","tid":1105570,"uid":56698,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T04:27:00.000Z","msg":"係都搵個重症外科醫生試下先啦<br />\n收皮啦光頭佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9a83552ed519a491e9533391c07264a96981d18","tid":1105570,"uid":44358,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T04:38:25.000Z","msg":"用民粹做神形式，帶領全台灣奶共<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a8950587